<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>Another way this is done, and there are certainly as many ways as there are guilds, is to have the pause built into the hotkey: <br /> <br />/2 Casting Cheal on &lt;--- %t ---&gt; <br />/cast6  <br />/cast6 (fizzle cast) <br />/pause 15 <br />/2 Go Go Go &lt;--- Next cleric in chain ---&gt; <br /> <br />The pause is predetermined by the chain or the cleric leading the chain and varies depending on the encounter.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
