<p>Always use the pause...  <br /> <br />you can't count on people to be able to count 1.2 seconds... <br /> <br />I always have a seperate window just for the Chain spam... <br /> <br />and here is my button set up <br /> <br />/Cast C# <br />/A# ----CH INC TO /%--------B# <br />/Cast C# <br />/Pause B# <br />/A# ------GO GO INSERT NEXT CLERIC -------B# <br /> <br /> <br /> <br />A# = Cleric Channel for chain spam <br />B# = Pause delay... 15 = 1.5 secs etc <br />C# = Gem # where Complete Heal is set <br /> <br />I cast first, then announce the CH then cast again... this gives just a moment more time to allow the first to fizzle and recover  if it is going to before the second cast is performed... NEVER put the second cast after the pause...   <br /></p>
